00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:11.970
And so, up front,
I just want to say

00:07:11.970 --> 00:07:15.630
that I see Donald Trump's
victory, and the Republicans

00:07:15.630 --> 00:07:20.270
broader victory, not as a
sharp break with the past,

00:07:20.270 --> 00:07:23.040
but as a culmination of
some fundamental trends

00:07:23.040 --> 00:07:25.170
in American politics
and policy that I want

00:07:25.170 --> 00:07:28.230
to talk with you about tonight.

00:07:28.230 --> 00:07:29.850
I also just want
to say how pleased

00:07:29.850 --> 00:07:33.480
I am to be able to
be here at Radcliffe.

00:07:33.480 --> 00:07:36.960
