00:07:49.260 --> 00:07:53.100
And one of the things I'm
going to be talking about today

00:07:53.100 --> 00:07:57.180
is the degree to
which the active state

00:07:57.180 --> 00:08:01.050
in the mid-20th century
increased our prosperity, not

00:08:01.050 --> 00:08:04.740
by redistributing, not by taking
from some and giving to others,

00:08:04.740 --> 00:08:07.140
but by opening up
opportunities that

00:08:07.140 --> 00:08:11.970
made our economy vastly more
productive, as well as vastly

00:08:11.970 --> 00:08:12.900
more fair.

00:08:12.900 --> 00:08:15.150
And that, I think, is really
symbolized by the role

00:08:15.150 --> 00:08:17.130
that Radcliffe has
played, historically,

00:08:17.130 --> 00:08:18.360
and continues to play today.

00:08:18.360 --> 00:08:20.760
And I'm honored to be
able to be a small part

00:08:20.760 --> 00:08:23.130
