00:45:29.860 --> 00:45:31.360
It can't just be another model.

00:45:31.360 --> 00:45:32.401
And I'm going to shut up.

00:45:32.401 --> 00:45:33.080
I see you.

00:45:33.080 --> 00:45:33.580
OK?

00:45:33.580 --> 00:45:34.560
But it's--

00:45:37.390 --> 00:45:39.940
- Well, I completely
take your first point.

00:45:42.470 --> 00:45:46.720
And I must say that it's
